### RoomHub Owner APIs Test Suite
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5143/api
@ownerEmail = owner@roomhub.vn
@password = Password123!

### 1. LOGIN TO OBTAIN JWT TOKEN
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{ownerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Save the Token from the login response
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 2. GET OWNER DASHBOARD SUMMARY
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. GET OWNER PROPERTY LIST
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. GET SINGLE PROPERTY DETAIL (FPT House ID=1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/properties/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. GET UNIT DETAIL (Room 101 ID=1, which is rented to Nguyễn Văn A)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/units/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. UPDATE UNIT OPERATIONAL STATUS (To Maintenance)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/owner/units/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Bảo trì"
}

### 7. UPDATE INTERNAL NOTES ON ROOM
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/units/1/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Khách báo sẽ đóng tiền muộn 2 ngày"
}

### 8. SEARCH ROOMHUB ACCOUNT FOR TENANT LINKING (Search tenant1@gmail.com)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/tenants/search?query=tenant1@gmail.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. GET ALL INVOICES FOR OWNER
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. GET SINGLE INVOICE DETAIL (Invoice ID=1, Month -2 paid invoice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/invoices/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. GET INVOICE DETAIL (Invoice ID=2, Month -1 unpaid invoice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/invoices/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. RECORD MANUAL PAYMENT (Ghi nhận thanh toán thủ công)
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/invoices/2/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 3500000,
  "paymentMethod": "BankTransfer",
  "transactionId": "FTX1293810238"
}

### 13. GET OWNER LISTINGS
GET {{baseUrl}}/owner/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
